Interface Editable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ValueChooserEditor<V>, ValueEditor<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSimpleValueEditor, BooleanValueEditor, CalendarValueEditor, CheckboxValueEditor, ComboBox, ComboBoxValueEditor, DoubleEntryField, Field, LocalizedObjectKeyFieldComponent, LocalizedTextEditor, NumberEditor, ProgrammaticIdentifierEditor, SearchableComboBox, TextEditor, ValueEditorAdaptor

    public interface Editable
    Indicates that a component is editable. An editable component can capture user generated content.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
